**Revenant** | Extra Elected | Haunted
__Basics__
When there is a Revenant, a banishment will take place on all odd days.
__Details__
The Revenant may choose to resign at any point during a phase, but will only lose the role at the end of the phase.
If there is no Revenant and a ghost election occurs, a Revenant is elected.
The Revenant gains an additional secret channel, which is reused for any subsequent Revenants.
The first night after being elected, the Revenant cannot be banished.

__Simplified__
The Revenant is elected before the poltergeist and the banshee.
When there is a Revenant, a banishment will take place on all odd days.
The first night after being elected, the Revenant cannot be banished.

__Formalized__
Ghostly Role
Passive Start Day: Create `Banishment` Poll in #graveyard_votes [Temporal: Day 3+] ⟨Odd: x1⟩
On Assigned: Protect @Self from `Banishments` through Passive Defense during Night (~UntilUse)
End Phase: {Vanishing} |silent:granting.resign|
  • Announce `@Self resigned as Revenant`
  • Revoke @ThisAttr from @Self

__Card__
The Revenant is elected to lead the graveyard.
